These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, german, pakistani
House: art-deco, ranch-style, cape-cod
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, rock
3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, canasta
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, cooking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, dahlia, bellflower
 1. the german is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the german is the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the art-deco house is the nigerian##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the pakistani is between the person playing scrabble and the person who growsbellflower##2
10. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
11. the art-deco house is the person playing canasta##1
12. the cape-cod house is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Nationality          | nigerian   | pakistani            | german     |
| House           | art-deco | cape-cod | ranch-style |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | rock               | r&b        |
| Game           | canasta        | chess         | scrabble   |
| Hobby         | cooking     | skydiving      | magic-tricks       |
| Flower     | bellflower        | dahlia              | daffodil       |

