.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester, game
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, red, turquise
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, october
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, woodening, parkour
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, snake
House: wooden, craftsman, farmhouse
 1. the person who likes green is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person who's sport is woodening is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who likes turquise is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the farmhouse house is between the person who likes green and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who likes red and the wooden house##2
 7. the game-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Cigar      | vegafina | ritmeester | game        |
| Color          | red   | turquise    | green        |
| Birthday   | january    | september | october |
| Sport   | parkour   | handball  | woodening         |
| Pet           | snake    | hedgehog | mouse       |
| House     | craftsman   | farmhouse    | wooden  |

