The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, marigold
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, van, car
House: craftsman, modern, farmhouse
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the electrician##1
 3. the electrician is on the left of the modern house##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the modern house and the entrepreneur##2
 6. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is the craftsman house##1
 9. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
10. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
11. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
12. the entrepreneur is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | sprite      | fanta        |
| Job         | entrepreneur   | electrician     | writer |
