.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, motorbike
3 different games are played: bridge, go, domino
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, september
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, amaryllis
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, pink, aquamarine
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who growsamaryllis##2
3. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
5. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
6. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person who likes turquise is between the person playing bridge and the person drinking juice##2
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice    | iced-tea           | 7up         |
| Transport         | motorbike   | taxi             | snowmobile  |
| Game           | domino  | go | bridge |
| Birthday   | january      | may              | september      |
| Flower   | amaryllis | rose             | zinnia     |
| Color         | pink   | turquise           | aquamarine      |

