.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
House: colonial, wooden, gothic-revival
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, western, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, mexican
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, almond-milk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, bellflower
City: hamburg, london, san-francisco
 1. the argentine is in an odd position##4
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 8. the mexican is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is the wooden house##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| House          | wooden    | gothic-revival  | colonial   |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | musical  | spy  |
| Nationality   | argentine | chinese  | mexican |
| Beverage           | coffee     | lemonade   | almond-milk   |
| Flower         | orchid  | rose | bellflower |
| City     | san-francisco   | hamburg      | london  |

