.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, dahlia
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, turquise
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, sports, western
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, soy-milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, roller
 1. the person who growsdaisy is the person driving the roller##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person watching western movies is the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
10. the person who likes ivory is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Pet          | ferret     | turtle   | mouse     |
| Flower         | dahlia | bellflower   | daisy  |
| Color           | grey   | turquise | ivory   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | sports       | western    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk        | iced-tea    | milk   |
| Transport         | van      | snowmobile     | roller |

 